{"id": "1279390649782898708", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 19, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "原本的災區就是要搞這個\n結果嘿\n綁等級上限道具", "timestamp": "2024-08-31T10:41:40.837000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["593627944979660800"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Coffee", "emoji_id": "1240919421791375380", "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1278599254188753050", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1279392255031119914", "channel_id": "1278075617228623872", "type": 19, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "我同意素材關不能太難\n但事實上最重要的道具主要產出在災區\n而災區對新手極度不友好\n主線的等級道具還是後來補的\n原本沒降低的難度也不是完全打不過或是極度凹\n就算無課玩久也能過\n主線也沒耗體力\n個人認為保留一些挑戰比較好", "timestamp": "2024-08-31T10:48:03.558000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1206976987621490729"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1279164599219785864", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1278075617228623872", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你遊核心玩法本質上是一種玩家們自發的玩家競賽（含大量個人觀點）", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174180524034637854"]}
